 Canada Investment Visa from India<\/strong><\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]<em>&#8220;How to apply for a Canada Investment Visa from India?&#8221;<\/em><\/p>\n<p>Investors worldwide flock to Canada for its growing economy and skilled workforce. This includes many Indian investors who settle in Canada with their families. Such people immigrate using one of the many <a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/canada-investment-visa-business-immigration\/\"><strong>Canada Investment Visa<\/strong><\/a> programs for investors the Canadian Government has introduced. This guide will cover how to immigrate to Canada from India as an investor.[\/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221;][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;padding-6-percent&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; centered_text=&#8221;true&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/1&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][nectar_btn size=&#8221;large&#8221; button_style=&#8221;regular&#8221; button_color_2=&#8221;Accent-Color&#8221; icon_family=&#8221;default_arrow&#8221; text=&#8221;Business Assessment for Investment Visa&#8221; url=&#8221;https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/business-immigration-assessment\/&#8221;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][vc_column_text]\n<h2 id=\"how-to\">How Does Canada Investment Visa Work?<\/h2>\n<p>There is no single Canada Investment Visa for Indian entrepreneurs. Instead, you will have a range of Canadian investment immigration programs. All of these programs have their unique eligibility requirements. Some may require you to invest amounts ranging from <strong>100,000 CAD<\/strong> to <strong>2 million CAD<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>However, the vast majority of Canada investor visa programs require you to make an investment and operate a business in Canada according to specific terms. Once you have done this, you will be eligible to apply for <a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/blog\/canada-pr-by-investment\/\"><strong>Canadian permanent residence through investment<\/strong><\/a>. Let\u2019s examine this in more detail below.[\/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; top_padding=&#8221;5%&#8221; bottom_padding=&#8221;5%&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221;][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color=&#8221;#96001c&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; colum