required for the investment typically starts from <strong>150,000 CAD<\/strong>. Additionally, your business must be profitable in India, and you must be:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Investor<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Entrepreneur\/Partner<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Self-Employed<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Senior Executive<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n[\/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]<strong>If you are an investor or an entrepreneur looking for licensed and experienced business immigration experts, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/contact-us\/\">get in touch with us here<\/a>.<\/strong>[\/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Key Eligibility Requirements for Canada Investment Visa&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_id=&#8221;requirements&#8221;][vc_column_text]The first step is to see if you are eligible for the Canada investment visa program you have chosen. There are many different requirements for these programs. This includes requirements related to:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Minimum Net Worth<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Minimum Investment<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Education<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Work Experience<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Business Ownership Experience<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Language Proficiency<\/strong><\/li>\n<li><strong>Age<\/strong><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Create a Business Plan<\/h3>\n<p>Once you have determined you are eligible for a specific business immigration program, you must create a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/blog\/the-importance-of-a-business-plan-for-canadian-business-immigration\/\"><strong>business plan<\/strong><\/a>. This business plan will need to include essential information about how you intend to set up your business and what activities the business will be involved with.<\/p>\n<p>The business plan is the most critical part of the application process, so you should ensure you create a comprehensive plan that convinces Canadian visa officers you can set up and operate a successful business.<\/p>\n<h3>Come to Canada and Operate Your Business<\/h3>\n<p>If you are chosen for a Canadian business immigration program, you will be issued a temporary work permit that allows you to come to Canada. You will also be required to sign a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.gov.nl.ca\/immigration\/files\/Sample-Business-Performance-Agreement.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>Business Performance Agreement<\/strong><\/a> (BPA) that describes the terms and conditions under which you must operate your business. Once in Canada, you must operate the business under the BPA terms for a specific time.<\/p>\n<h3>Apply for Permanent Residence<\/h3>\n<p>When you have successfully met the terms of your agreement, you can apply for permanent residence. This way, you can obtain Canada PR by Investment.[\/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner equal_height=&#8221;yes&#8221; content_placement=&#8221;middle&#8221; column_margin=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_tablet=&#8221;default&#8221; column_direction_phone=&#8221;default&#8221; top_padding=&#8221;5%&#8221; bottom_padding=&#8221;5%&#8221; text_align=&#8221;left&#8221;][vc_column_inner column_padding=&#8221;no-extra-padding&#8221; column_padding_tablet=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_phone=&#8221;inherit&#8221; column_padding_position=&#8221;all&#8221; column_element_spacing=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color=&#8221;#96001c&#8221; background_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; background_hover_color_opacity=&#8221;1&#8243; column_shadow=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_radius=&#8221;none&#8221; column_link_target=&#8221;_self&#8221; gradient_direction=&#8221;left_to_right&#8221; overlay_strength=&#8221;0.3&#8243; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; tablet_width_inherit=&#8221;default&#8221; bg_image_animation=&#8221;none&#8221; border_type=&#8221;simple&#8221; column_border_width=&#8221;none&#8221; column_border_style=&#8221;solid&#8221;][image_with_animation image_url=&#822