r Canadian Business Immigration<\/h3>\n<p>Our Licensed Experts smoothly handle the entire process, including the business plan, paperwork, and PR application.[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][nectar_btn size=&#8221;large&#8221; open_new_tab=&#8221;true&#8221; button_style=&#8221;regular&#8221; button_color_2=&#8221;Accent-Color&#8221; icon_family=&#8221;none&#8221; text=&#8221;Get in touch with us&#8221; url=&#8221;https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/contact-us\/&#8221; margin_top=&#8221;20px&#8221;][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Benefits of Canada Investment Visa&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221; el_id=&#8221;benefits&#8221;][vc_column_text]These are some benefits that you get with Canada Investment Visa from India:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Live in Canada with your family<\/li>\n<li>Get an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/open-work-permit\/\"><strong>Open Work Permit<\/strong><\/a> for your spouse<\/li>\n<li>Free education for children in the Canadian public school system<\/li>\n<li>Processing times range from 3 months to 24 months<\/li>\n<li>Get Canadian PR and Citizenship through investment<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n[\/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=&#8221;Need help?&#8221; use_theme_fonts=&#8221;yes&#8221;][vc_column_text]<a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/book-consultation\/business-immigration\/\"><strong>Book a Business Strategy Meeting<\/strong><\/a> with our licensed experts if you\u2019re interested in applying for an investment visa to Canada from India. Our team is led by <strong>Mr. Keshav Sharma,<\/strong> a Regulated Canadian Immigration Consultant familiar with the various pathways to acquiring Canadian citizenship for investment for Indian residents. We can guide you in choosing the correct Canada investment visa from India.<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.elaarimmigration.ca\/blog\/immigrate-to-canada-as-an-investor\/\"><strong>5 Ways to Immigrate to Canada as an Investor<\/strong><\/a><\/li>\n<li><a href